textBody:
EAN may refer to:

* Emergency Action Notification, an American nationwide activation of the Emergency Alert System
* Enriched air nitrox
* Ethylammonium nitrate, a salt and ionic liquid
* European Academy of Neurology
* International Article Number (originally European Article Number)
* European Aviation Network, a satellite and LTE broadband network for airplanes under development by Inmarsat
